SetInCountry: Canada
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Wamika Katoch
AuthorCountry: Canada
Text: I am a video creator and blogger. I love travelling and exploring new places
  and write my experience during my journey. Travelling helps me a lot in discovering
  myself as well and since my childhood I had this innate love for travelling new
  places in order to experience life beyond the limits.  Just like a leap into the
  unknown, which gives me a thrilling experience .
